title: Vote Carson Wentz For Rookie Of The Year
text:
Related: Watch: Carson Wentz Micâ€™d Up For Cowboys Game 
Wentz completed a franchise record 379 passes. He also set a team rookie record for passing yards (3,782), completion percentage (62.4) and passing touchdowns (16). 
Carson Wentz has won rookie of the week in Weeks 1, 3, and 5 and won offensive rookie of the month for September . The other finalists for the award are Dak Prescott (DAL), Ezekiel Elliott (DAL), Deion Jones (ATL), and Joey Bosa (SD).
